title: Is Cassie The Only One With These Irrational Fears?
description:
Cassie's anxiety is at an all time high, and it started to get worse around the fourth of July. During this time, she had a new fear unlocked when she read a story about a stray bullet from a gun someone fired into the air falling from the sky and killing someone. 
This triggered all of her irrational fears, and she quickly realized I have a lengthy list. Is this a sign it's time for her to start anxiety meds?
